                        <p>抑或是远赴大洋彼岸的志愿者行动，</p>
                        <p>UIN为你力荐社会实践，</p>
                        <p>不仅为了申请，</p>
                        <p>更为了绚烂你的青春。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="left col-xs-6">
                    <img src="${req.contextPath}/resources/fiveAdvantages/uinHelp/ngo.png">
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li class="section3">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="left col-xs-6">
                    <div class="text-column">
                        <p class="subTitle">顶级名校科研项目
                        <div class="icon">
                            <img src="${req.contextPath}/resources/fiveAdvantages/uinHelp/3g.png">
                        </div>
